#. type: Plain text
#: 2021-02-09-global-newsletter-48.md:202
msgid ""
"XR Norway is calling for rebels to stand in solidarity with the 53 Norweigan "
"rebels who are standing trial for blockading the country’s Oil and Energy "
"Ministry last year."
